der komendant iz arayngekumen

00:20:33.743 --> 00:20:36.606
un er hot gezogt tsu mir, "UNK, gut morgn!"

00:20:36.763 --> 00:20:39.220
azoy arumet flegn zey dokh gornisht zogn keyn gut morgn.

00:20:39.312 --> 00:20:40.217
hot mikh,

00:20:40.257 --> 00:20:42.191
