ikh hob gegebn a, ikh hob gezen, ikh hob ergets gekoyft a fleshl bronfn bay eynem, vos iz fun ⟨Patsholek⟩, eyn,

00:20:48.083 --> 00:20:53.584
ikh zol kenen opbakrign mayn mayn mayn SALARY khotsh, ikh hob op- on dem hot men gornisht bakumen kimat.

00:20:53.584 --> 00:20:54.898
m'hot dokh gegebn nor tsu esn.

00:20:55.208 --> 00:20:56.282
ikh hob genumen,

00:20:56.355 --> 00:20:59.015
ikh hob aroyfgeleygt di por shmates vos m'hot gehat,

00:20:59.933 --> 00:21:02.301
oyf a vegele, a poyerish vegele,

00:21:02.301 --> 00:21:03.153
hot zikh geshlept

00:21:03.153 --> 00:21:06.097
lebn breg fun vaser, kedey zol, s'hot nisht gehat keyn reder.

00:21:06.097 --> 00:21:07.521
kedey m'zol tsukumen biz.

00:21:07.628 --> 00:21:10.372
bin ikh tsugekumen tsu an andere vaser, hot es geheysn Vim.

00:21:11.020 --> 00:21:15.604
azoy vi Suets Kanal UNK zikh, un iz do shtark shturmish.

00:21:15.627 --> 00:21:16.937
groyse taykhn.

00:21:17.449 --> 00:21:19.080
ikh bin ariber oyf yene zayt,

00:21:19.305 --> 00:21:20.576
oyf yene zayt taykh.

00:21:20.576 --> 00:21:22.353
alts in Komi A.S.S.R.

00:21:22.495 --> 00:21:24.463
dos di nekht, vayse nekht,

00:21:24.587 --> 00:21:27.298
m'veyst nisht tsu s'nekhtn tsi s'haynt tsi s'morgn.

00:21:28.063 --> 00:21:29.491
ikh zits dort,

00:21:29.886 --> 00:21:34.942
