00:21:35.134 --> 00:21:39.549
vu zi vet forn for ikh, fort zi nokh vayter vel ikh oykh forn, abi ikh vel zayn in a shtot.

00:21:39.859 --> 00:21:42.890
s'dokh al-kol-ponem Siktefka hot geheysn di shtot.

00:21:42.981 --> 00:21:45.113
oder in der zayt loyf es oyf Moskve,

00:21:45.113 --> 00:21:47.582
nenter tsum, tsu dem, keyn dorem,

00:21:47.908 --> 00:21:49.286
tsu di vareme lender.

00:21:49.798 --> 00:21:51.429
dos goyrl hot azoy gevolt,

00:21:51.553 --> 00:21:53.487
az ikh zol oykh forn keyn Siktefka,

00:21:53.578 --> 00:21:54.601
dort ahin.

00:21:55.249 --> 00:21:58.938
engshaft! oysergeveyntlekh!

00:22:00.480 --> 00:22:02.735
m'pakt zikh un s'geferlekh.

