mayns a mume hot gehat farloyrn epes a valizkele, hot zi gehat dort altsding, zi hot dokh nokh gehat, zi iz dokh geven a froy, hot zi gehat alesding.

00:22:08.931 --> 00:22:10.548
nu, ikh hob epes opgefunen.

00:22:11.145 --> 00:22:13.586
ikh ken aykh zogn, ikh bin iberal borkhashem

00:22:13.913 --> 00:22:15.476
geven oyfn plats.

00:22:16.073 --> 00:22:17.619
ikh bin aroyfgekumen oyf di shif,

00:22:17.710 --> 00:22:22.665
di letste shif iz dos geven vos iz shoyn aroysgeforn, az nisht iz do vinter, s'tsit zikh di gantse leng.

00:22:23.194 --> 00:22:24.369
mir forn,

00:22:24.814 --> 00:22:29.063
hob ikh mitgenumen azoy, ikh hob gehat kaloshn, ir veyst vos heyst kaloshn? hob ikh opgeshnitn

00:22:29.063 --> 00:22:30.776
di kaloshn oyf azoy fil,

00:22:30.776 --> 00:22:32.058
vayl do iz geven tserisn,

00:22:32.058 --> 00:22:36.724
shpeter az ikh zol hobn tsu tsubindn mit a shtrikl, tomer hob ikh nisht keyn shikh shpeter, ikh hob gehat, ikh hob nokh gehat

00:22:36.724 --> 00:22:40.501
a mantl, ober dos mantl hob ikh nokh gehaltn azoy arumet ineveynik, ikh hob nisht gehat.

00:22:41.571 --> 00:22:44.259
a klal, shoyn,

00:22:44.259 --> 00:22:47.465
ze ikh, kuk ikh on, ikh hob nokh on- ikh hob nokh, ikh hob ikh ongegreyt

00:22:47.465 --> 00:22:52.145
fun broyt vos ikh hob gehat, hob ikh nokh genumen dos dare shtikele broyt, hob ikh gemakht a zekele dare shtiklekh.

00:22:52.540 --> 00:22:54.832
fun shoyn lang, di ale mol avekgeleygt a shtikele,

00:22:54.832 --> 00:22:56.398
un dos hob ikh genumen oyfn veg,

00:22:56.421 --> 00:23:00.144
ikh bin aroyfgekumen oyf dem oyfn vaser, hob ikh getrofn nokh ot a yid.

00:23:00.657 --> 00:23:03.840
dos ershte iz geven ven ikh hob im gefregt, host efsher a kalendar.

00:23:04.015 --> 00:23:08.551
ikh hob gevust ven s'iz peysekh, ven s'iz dos, alesding, nor ikh hob gevolt a shtikl kalendar.

00:23:08.551 --> 00:23:10.424
a nisht keyn a gemakhtn vi do,

00:23:10.424 --> 00:23:11.703
a geshribene.

00:23:13.380 --> 00:23:15.449
mir forn, m'zetst zikh oyf,

00:23:15.473 --> 00:23:16.631
m'kumt tsu,

00:23:16.890 --> 00:23:20.326
kumt tsu tsu Kotlas, tsum zelbn plats vu m'iz geforn aher,

00:23:20.383 --> 00:23:21.592
ze'mir tsurik gekumen.

00:23:21.801 --> 00:23:23.314
m'iz gekumen aher,

00:23:24.197 --> 00:23:27.164
nu, geyt men arop. vos tut men? gey ikh aroys oyfn oyfn mark,

00:23:27.164 --> 00:23:28.244
gebn a kuk,

