ikh muz koyfn a vogn.

00:24:07.093 --> 00:24:13.617
shoyn geven, vayl ikh hob shoyn gehat a geshikhte fun a sakh mentshn, ale bakante, di mishpokhe, di dos zenen gekumen, alts iz gelign oyf di UNK.

00:24:14.029 --> 00:24:15.930
ikh hob gekoyft a vogn, gedenk ikh,

00:24:16.307 --> 00:24:22.173
far far tsvey toyznt rubl, der rubl iz dokh geven nisht azoy gehoybn, iz dokh gornisht gevezn, azoy hot gekost bay di bay di

00:24:22.332 --> 00:24:23.558
bay di stantsye,

00:24:24.508 --> 00:24:26.105
un m'zetst zikh arayn.

