00:24:46.400 --> 00:24:49.764
dos, m'ligt un got tsu danken, m'fort aroys.

00:24:51.660 --> 00:24:53.645
un den kumt on a rusishe tsug,

00:24:54.208 --> 00:24:55.670
fun Rusland, fun Moskve.

